[Reaver Modifier Codes\Press L1 + D-Pad Up To Activate The Dark Reaver]
author=InterAct
description=<P>The Reaver Modifier codes CAN cause problems if activated too early on in the game.
Some cinemas will lock up if you activate certain Reavers BEFORE you activate the forges! If you've already activated all of the forges, they'll work fine. (Using these codes will also activate the Elemental Fonts found throughout the game, even if the forges are NOT active.)</P> <P>Now Raziel can use the Fire, Wind, Dark and Light Reavers in the spectral realm as well as the Physical Realm!</P>
patch=1,EE,D026CAC0,extended,0000FBEF
patch=1,EE,10241C68,extended,00001000
patch=1,EE,D026CACC,extended,0000FBEF
patch=1,EE,10241C68,extended,00001000

[Press L3 To Become Invincible]
author=InterAct
description=You'll need to deactivate Invincibility the first time you enter the Spectral Realm. Once you've regained your health in the Spectral Realm, and are able to shift back to the Physical Realm, reactivate Invincibility. Once this is done, you'll be able to shift back and forth without any trouble.
patch=1,EE,D026CAC0,extended,0000FFFD
patch=1,EE,1023BAD4,extended,00000000

